ם רו ך  / for with you is the fountain of all life, in your light do
we behold all light. The flow of light represented by the tallit is joined to
the blessing of life itself. God is described here in the psalmistòs most deli-
cate and abstract phrasing. We reach forth to the source of life and are
bathed in its light as it flows forth to meet us.    /SC/XXA.G./XX/PR

